Kasancewar kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) da ke ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, Janairu 1 zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Kasuwancin kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ya nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya wanda ya tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa matakan sun bambanta dangane da ƙasa, cutar COVID-19 tana haɓaka cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, jihohi, asibitoci, da kuma cibiyoyin gaggawa suna bukatar su kara shirye-shiryen su don karuwar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da za su bukaci kulawar lafiya, musamman ma na gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wani tarin cututtukan cutar huhu da ba a san asalinsa ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar kasar Sin ta ruwaito cewa sabon coronavirus ne wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus cuta mai tsanani ta numfashi 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaidar da aka samu har zuwa yanzu ta nuna cewa kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 suna da wata cuta mai sauƙi, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin mutanen da ke fama da cutar sun warke.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin dari na shari'o'in, COVID-19 ya zama mummunan cuta kuma yana buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari na shari'o'in ke fama da mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti sakamakon COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun bincika yanayin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sannan muka kwatanta su da abubuwan da suka faru a lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu dauke da cutar COVID-19 a kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya da adadin wadanda suka kamu da ita a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Kasuwancin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya sami ƙarin yaduwar ƙasa kuma tasirin cutar COVID-19 a sauran sassan duniya yana bin tasirin cutar a China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin Eurosurveillance 2020 na 5 ga Maris, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon Turawa da suka tabbatar da COVID-19 dangane da ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta fara bayar da rahoton mutum uku da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da Burtaniya (UK), tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da 15 ga Maris, 2020 tare da waɗannan kwanakin, akwai shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 da aka ruwaito, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun adadi na COVID-19 da kuma adadi na al'amura
A Cibiyar Tsare Kariya da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da kowace ƙasa a duniya ta ruwaito kowace rana da karfe 8.00.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan ne don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta shi da yanayin Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na yaduwar cutar COVID-19 mai aiki, mun lissafa lokutan da aka rage na kwanaki 14, don haka muna la'akari da tafiya ta al'ada ta COVID-19, a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a cikin lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jimlar adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito a kowace ƙasa zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8.00 na dare idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Kasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun bi halin da ake ciki a lardin Hubei (Tiongkok) (Hotuna na 1).
Ga EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya gaba ɗaya, adadin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan ya ƙaru sosai a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (Ƙarin Bayani).
Wannan yanayin yafi karuwa da sauri a cikin adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwar abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 (Karin Bayani).
Hoton 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya idan aka kwatanta da adadin da aka samu a Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Bayanai sun nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00, sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA 15 da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin shari'o'in da suka yi daidai da adadin Italiya na makonni uku da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Hanyoyin da aka lura da abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ƙaruwa a daidai wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya faru ne duk da bambancin matakan da ƙasashe ke fuskanta, bambancin amsawar lafiyar jama'a, da kuma yiwuwar bambancin ma'anar shari'a tsakanin ƙasashe da bambancin yarjejeniya don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, wanda ya haɗa da gwaji na gaba.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankin Italiya da ke fama da cutar sun bayyana halin da ake ciki na kimanin kashi 10 cikin dari na marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da wuraren kula da gaggawa a yankin sun kai ga iyakar ƙarfin su.
A halin yanzu, bayanan karɓar shari'ar COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa mai tsanani a matakin EU/EAA kawai suna samuwa ga kashi 6% da 1% na shari'ar (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara bayanai a cikin tsari don a kammala bayanan kulawa na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Binciken da aka yi a shekara ta 2010 zuwa 2011 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin samun gado mai tsanani da kuma kula da lafiya a Turai, yana daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe za su iya samun albarkatu da yawa ko kaɗan fiye da Italiya (12.5 wuraren kwana na kulawa mai tsanani da kulawa ta jiki a kowace 100,000 na yawan jama'a a cikin 2010-2011).
An ba da labarin yanayin yanayin yanayin yanayin yanayin yanayin yanayin yanayin COVID-19 na kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da UK wanda ke da haɗarin > 90% fiye da ƙarfin kwanciyar hankali, a cikin sabuntawar ECDC ta shida game da COVID-19.
Tun da yake har yanzu ana tattara shari'o'i a wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da wuraren kulawa da gaggawa suna yawanci bauta wa yawan jama'a a cikin wani yanki na sabis, ya kamata a samar da bayani game da shari'o'i da wuraren kula da gaggawa a matakin Sunan Sashin Yankin don Statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana tasowa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, jihohi, asibitoci, da kuma cibiyoyin gaggawa ya kamata su shirya kansu don yanayin watsawar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kula da lafiya, musamman ma kula da gaggawa, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da aka shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin binciken ECDC na kwanan nan, hanzari, mai aiki, da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar da za a yi amfani da ita don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauyawa daga hanyar dakatarwa zuwa hanyar ragewa, saboda ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin adadin shari'o'in, kamar yadda aka yi tsammani, bazai ba da isasshen lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don fahimta, karɓa, da daidaitawa da amsa mai dacewa ba idan ba a yi amfani da shi ba a baya.
Wannan saurin kimantawa na haɗari ya kuma haɗa da matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
