Shekaru: Shekaru shine mafi mahimmancin sanarwa ga SARS, wanda kuma ya shafi COVID-19.
COVID-19 ya fi faruwa a cikin shekaru 30 zuwa 65 tare da kashi 47.7% na marasa lafiya a cikin shekaru 50 da haihuwa a cikin binciken da ya ƙunshi shari'o'i 8,866 kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama.
Marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani suna da haɗari da haɗari da kuma rikitarwa kuma suna da shekaru masu yawa fiye da marasa lafiya da ba su buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani (mai matsakaici shekaru 66 fiye da shekaru 51), wanda ke nuna cewa shekaru sune abubuwan da ke haifar da sakamakon ƙarshe na marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Jima'i: SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kamuwa da maza fiye da mata (0.31/100,000 fiye da 0.27/100,000), kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama.
Haɗuwa da cututtuka: Marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani na COVID-19 suna da mafi yawan haɗarin ciwon zuciya da arrhythmia.
Har ila yau, cututtukan zuciya ne ke haifar da mutuwar mutane da ke fama da cutar SARS.
An ruwaito cewa SARS-CoV-2 na iya haɗuwa da colangiocytes masu kyau na ACE2, wanda zai iya haifar da rashin aikin hanta a cikin marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Ya kamata mu lura cewa shekaru da kuma cututtukan da ke tattare da su suna da alaƙa sosai kuma suna iya shafan juna.
Abubuwan da aka gano a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje: Yawan C-reactive protein (CRP) a cikin jini yana nuna cewa ƙwayar cuta ko rauni na ƙwayoyin cuta yana da tsanani kuma an ba da shawarar cewa yana da tasiri ga yanayin rashin lafiya, amsa ga magani, da kuma farfadowa.
An kuma gabatar da wani dangantaka tsakanin matakan CRP da kuma mummunan cutar da kuma hangen nesa na COVID-19.
Bugu da ƙari, ƙara yawan lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), da kuma creatinine kinase (CK) na iya taimakawa wajen hango ko hasashen sakamakon ƙarshe.
Waɗannan enzymes suna bayyana sosai a gabobin jiki, musamman a zuciya da kuma zuciya, kuma suna fitowa daga jikin mutum yayin da ake lalata kayan.
Saboda haka, waɗannan enzymes sun zama alamun gargajiya na rashin aikin zuciya da hanta.
Babban alamun asibiti: Dole ne a yi la'akari da hotunan thorax da ci gaban alamun asibiti na lokaci tare da sauran abubuwa don hango ƙarshen sakamakon da rikitarwa na COVID-19.
Amfani da Steroids: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, steroids suna da iko da rigakafi da ake amfani da su sosai a matsayin magani mai taimako don cututtukan cututtuka don rage mummunan lalacewar kumburi.
Saboda ana amfani da corticosteroids masu yawa a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani na SARS, mutane da yawa da suka tsira daga wannan cuta sun ƙare da shan wahala daga osteonecrosis avascular tare da nakasa ta rayuwa da rashin ingancin rayuwa.
Saboda haka, idan ya cancanta, ya kamata a yi amfani da steroids a ƙananan allurai da gajeren lokaci a cikin marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Matsin hankali: Kamar yadda aka bayyana a sama, a lokacin barkewar COVID-19, marasa lafiya da yawa suna fama da matsanancin damuwa saboda sun shiga cikin dogon lokaci na keɓewa da matsanancin rashin tabbas da kuma mutuwar dangi da abokan marasa lafiya.
