Shaidar filogenetik ta nuna cewa bats da rodents sune tushen tushen asalin mafi yawan alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune manyan wuraren ajiyar gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoVs sun ci gaba da ƙetare ƙuntatawa na nau'in, kuma wasu CoVs sun zama manyan cututtuka a cikin mutane.
A halin yanzu, an san mutum bakwai da suka kamu da cutar korona.
Daga cikin waɗannan ƙwayoyin guda bakwai, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoV.
Sauran beta-CoV guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cutar korona ta rikicin numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), cutar korona ta rikicin numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da kuma SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da bayyanar cututtuka masu sauƙi, kamar mura da/ko fitsari.
A akasin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV, da SARS-CoV-2 suna da cututtuka masu yawa, suna haifar da cututtukan ƙananan huhu a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa kuma suna da mafi girma damar ci gaba da cutar ta rashin numfashi (ARDS) da bayyanar cututtukan huhu.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko, B814, daga cikin marasa lafiya masu cutar a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar zurfin nazarin HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, duka biyun suna haifar da bayyanar cututtuka da kansu.
A gaskiya ma, an yarda da wannan ra'ayi cewa kamuwa da cutar HCoV ba ta da haɗari, har sai an sami barkewar cutar SARS.
Cutar SARS da ta auku a shekara ta 2003 na ɗaya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi halakarwa a tarihin zamani, wanda ya shafi mutane fiye da 8,000 tare da yawan mutuwar kusan 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, annobar cutar ta cutar ta Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS) ta haifar da ci gaba da yaduwar cutar a yankin Larabawa tare da yaduwar cutar zuwa sauran sassan duniya.
Sabon HCoV 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda aka sake kira SARS-CoV-2, shine mai haifar da cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wanda ya kashe mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ya kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadi kuma dole ne duniya ta shirya don cutar SARS-CoV-2 mai zuwa.
Dukkanin HCoVs bakwai na zoonotic ne daga bats, beraye, ko dabbobi.
Akwai hujjoji da yawa da suka nuna cewa dukkanin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga bats. A bats, CoVs suna daidaitawa sosai kuma ba su da cututtuka, amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta mai yawa.
Cutar COVID-19 ta kawo gagarumin kalubale na kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa, da kuma ɗabi'a ga kasar Sin da sauran duniya.
Bin diddigin asalin HCoV na zoonotic yana ba da tsarin fahimtar tarihin halitta, motsi, da kuma ƙuntataccen abubuwan da ke haifar da yaduwar tsakanin jinsuna.
