A cikin shekaru da dama da suka gabata, an gano HCoVs bakwai.
A takaice taƙaitaccen tarihin gano HCoV a cikin jerin jerin abubuwa (Table 1) yana da bayani.
An fara ware nau'in HCoV-229E daga cikin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar ta sama a shekara ta 1966, wanda aka yi amfani da shi don girma a cikin WI-38 cell line.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da cutar HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun cutar ta tsatsa, wanda ya hada da ciwon kai, kumburi, kumburi, da kuma ciwon wuya, tare da zazzabi da tari wanda ya bayyana a 10~20% na lokuta.
Daga baya a 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun kwayoyin halitta da kuma jerin hanyoyin a cikin kwakwalwar da ke shan nono.
Bayanan asibiti na kamuwa da cutar HCoV-OC43 ya yi kama da kamuwa da cutar da HCoV-229E ke haifarwa, wanda ba a iya bambanta shi da sauran cututtukan huhu kamar cutar mura ta A da rhinovirus ba.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 sun bazu ko'ina cikin duniya kuma suna iya kamuwa da su a lokacin hunturu a yankuna masu matsakaicin yanayi.
Yawancin lokaci, waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu suna da tsawon lokaci na ƙasa da mako guda, kuma suna da tsawon lokaci na rashin lafiya na kusan makonni biyu.
Bisa ga binciken da aka yi na masu aikin sa kai a kan mutane, mutane masu lafiya da suka kamu da cutar HCoV-229E sun kamu da cutar taƙama mai sauƙi.
Mutane da yawa ba su da lafiya sosai, amma suna da tsarin rigakafi da ya raunana.
SARS, wanda aka fi sani da "pneumonia atipis", shine farkon cutar ta HCoV da aka rubuta sosai a tarihin ɗan adam kuma wakili na etiological shine SARS-CoV, wanda shine HCoV na uku da aka gano.
An gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong, China.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da shari'o'i 8,096 da aka ruwaito tare da mutuwar 774, wanda ya bazu a ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Ba tare da an yi amfani da su ba, ana kiyasta cewa kowace cuta za ta iya haifar da wasu cututtuka na biyu, tare da lokacin yin amfani da kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 da kuma ganin ƙwayar cuta a ranar 10 na kamuwa da cutar.
Marasa lafiya da suka kamu da SARS-CoV sun fara fama da cutar ta myalgia, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin ƙarfi, da kuma yin rawar jiki, wanda aka bi da shi da dyspnea, tari, da kuma rashin numfashi a matsayin ci gaba da bayyanar cututtuka.
Lymphopenia, gwajin hanta da kuma karuwa a cikin creatine kinase, wani abu ne da ake yawan gani a cikin SARS.
Ana kuma lura da lalacewar alveolar diffusion, yaduwar epithelial cells, da kuma karuwa a cikin macrophage a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS.
Bayan haka, kashi 20-30 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani da kuma iska mai iska.
Ban da ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, wasu gabobin da suka shafi gastrointestinal tract, hanta, da koda suna iya kamuwa da cutar a cikin matsanancin yanayi, yawanci tare da hadari na cytokine, wanda zai iya zama mai mutuwa, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da rauni.
An fara ware kwayar daga wani kwayar cutar da aka yi wa wani mutum a cikin huhu wanda ya zo Hong Kong daga birnin Guangzhou.
Tun daga lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai don nazarin HCoV.
An killace HCoV-NL63 daga yara masu watanni 7 daga Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
A farko, wannan ƙwayar tana da yawa a cikin yara, tsofaffi, da kuma marasa lafiya da ke fama da cututtukan numfashi.
Ana samun cututtukan coryza, conjunctivitis, zazzabi, da bronchiolitis a cikin cututtukan da HCoV-NL63 ke haifarwa.
Wani bincike na musamman ya bayyana cewa an ware wannan kwayar daga nasal na wani dan shekara takwas da ke fama da cutar huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a Netherlands, amma a gaskiya, cutar ta bazu ko'ina cikin duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 yana wakiltar kusan kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun kuma yana da ƙaruwa a farkon bazara, bazara, da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da laryngitis na hanawa, wanda ake kira kuma croup.
A wannan shekarar, an killace HCoV-HKU1 daga wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka yi masa asibiti saboda cutar huhu da bronchiolitis a Hong Kong.
