A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19 da ke faruwa a matsayin cuta ta coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar "zazzabin cuta" tana nufin yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda cutar ta yi muni ba, WHO ta lura da bukatar ƙarfafa gwamnatoci su yi aiki:
Dukkanin kasashe na iya canza yanayin annobar.
Idan jihohi suka gano, suka gwada, suka magance, suka ware, kuma suka yi wa al'ummarsu aiki a matsayin martani, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Mun yi hattara sosai saboda yawan yaduwar da kuma mummunan halin da ake ciki da kuma rashin jinkirin da ake ciki.
A cewar Dr. Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka a Amirka, wannan annoba "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
A wani rahoto da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, ta ce, "ba a taɓa bin diddigin wani kwayar cutar da ta shafi numfashi ba, banda cutar influenza, daga lokacin da ta fara zuwa ci gaba da yaduwar ta duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya yi irin wannan furucin, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar coronavirus ba".
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci guda ba".
Sabuwar annobar ta biyo bayan wani hukunci na WHO a watan Janairu wanda ya bayyana cutar a matsayin wata matsala ta lafiyar jama'a da ke damun duniya.
Dokta Anthony Fauci, shugaban Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Ƙasar Amirka, ya ce game da annobar, "ainihin, za ta yi muni".
