An tabbatar da kasancewar cutar a cikin samfurin ta hanyar RT-PCR, wanda ke gano RNA na coronavirus.
Wannan gwaji na musamman ne kuma an tsara shi ne don gano RNA na SARS-CoV-2 kawai.
