A shekara ta 2008, wani bincike da Jami'ar Westminster ta gudanar, a London, kuma masana'antar ta tallafa wa taron taro na Turai, ya kwatanta yawan tsabtace takarda, bushewar iska mai dumi, da kuma bushewar iska mai zamani.
