Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa a ware marasa lafiya da ke zuwa zuwa a cikin ɗakunan jiran daban-daban dangane da idan ana zargin su da cutar COVID-19. Baya ga sauran APDs, OSHA ta ba da shawarar masu numfashi ga mutanen da ke aiki a cikin nisan ƙafa 6 daga marasa lafiya da aka sani ko ake zargin suna da cutar SARS-CoV-2, da mutanen da ke yin aikin samar da aerosol.
A Amurka, an amince da N95 mai tsabta na fuska mai tsabta na fuska ko mafi kyau don amfani a cikin tsarin rubutaccen shirin kariya na numfashi wanda ya haɗa da gwajin dacewa, horo, da kuma duba likita.
