B'Angiotensin 2 (ACE2) mai canzawa enzyme ne wanda yake haɗe da farfajiya na waje (membrane) a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana da aiki na gaba da na angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE), ta hanyar rage yawan angiotensin-II da kuma kara Angiotensin (1-7), yana mai da shi wata manufa mai ban sha'awa don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin shigarwa zuwa cikin kwayoyin halitta don wasu coronavirus.
Ana kiran juyin halitta na ɗan adam na ACE2 hACE2.
Angiotensin 2 mai juyawa enzyme ne mai dauke da zinc wanda yake a farfajiyar endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Protein ACE2 yana da yankin M2 na terminal-N peptidase da kuma yankin transporter na terminal-C na renal amino acid collectrin.
ACE2 shine furotin mai ɗaukar hoto guda ɗaya na nau'in I, tare da yankin aiki mai aiki wanda aka fallasa a saman sel a cikin huhu da sauran kayan.
Ƙungiyar ACE2 ta cire daga cikin ƙwayoyin transmembrane ta wani enzyme, wanda aka sani da sheddase, kuma an saki furotin mai narkewa a cikin jini kuma an fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin mafi yawan gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana haɗe da membranes na ƙwayoyin halitta musamman na ƙwayoyin cuta na huhu na nau'i na II, ƙwayoyin gut, ƙwayoyin endothelial na arteries da veins, da ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jini a mafi yawan gabobin jiki.
Ana kuma samun ACE2 mRNA a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine daidaita ACE.
ACE ta raba hormone angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II na vasosuccontraction.
A ƙarshe, ACE2 ta yanke amino acid phenylalanine na karboxyl terminal daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma ta hydrolyzed shi zuwa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7) (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma yana iya karya wasu peptides ciki har da [des-Arg9] -bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita zirga-zirgar membrane na amino acid SLC6A19 wanda ba shi da amfani kuma yana da hannu a cikin cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai transmembrane, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban shigarwa a cikin sel don wasu coronavirus, wanda ya haɗa da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus wanda ke haifar da SARS); da kuma SARS-CoV-2 (virus wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
Ƙari ga haka, haɗuwa da furotin S1 a spike ko spike na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 tare da yankin ACE2 enzymatic a saman sel yana haifar da endositosis da kuma canzawar ƙwayoyin cuta da enzymes zuwa endosomes da ke cikin sel.
Wannan tsarin shigar da kwayar cutar yana buƙatar priming na S-protein ta hanyar TMPRSS2 mai karɓar bakuncin protease serine, wanda ake bincike a halin yanzu don hana shi a matsayin magani mai yiwuwa.
Duk da haka, yawancin masana da kuma hukumomi suna ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE da ARB na yau da kullum.
Wani bincike da aka yi a kan tsarin da kuma nazarin da aka yi, wanda aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa "amfani da masu hana ACE ya haifar da raguwa mai muhimmanci na 34% a cikin hadarin cutar ta huhu idan aka kwatanta da na iko".
Bugu da ƙari, "amfani da masu hana ACEs ya rage haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar, musamman waɗanda ke fama da bugun jini da rashin zuciya.
Ana kuma danganta amfani da ACE inhibitors da rage yawan mutuwar da ke tattare da cutar huhu, ko da yake sakamakon bai da ƙarfi idan aka kwatanta da haɗarin cutar huhu gaba ɗaya".
Ana tsammanin ACE2 na mutum (rhACE2) zai zama sabon magani don cututtukan huhu na gaggawa, kuma yana da alama yana haɓaka haemodynamics na huhu da kuma saturated oxygen a cikin alade tare da cututtukan huhu na gaggawa wanda lipoplysaccharides ke haifar.
RHACE2 yana da rabin lokaci na kimanin sa'o'i 10 a cikin mutum tare da aiki na minti 30 ban da tsawon sa'o'i 24.
Wasu binciken sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai ban sha'awa ga marasa lafiya da ba su yarda da tsarin renin-angiotensin (RAS) na gargajiya ba ko kuma a cikin cututtuka da angiotensin II a cikin jini ya karu. An gwada rhACE2 a cikin gwaji na asibiti don maganin cututtukan huhu.
b'Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikace ne na wayar hannu wanda aka tsara don taimakawa bin diddigin lamba don magance cutar coronavirus ta 2019-2020, wato, tsarin gano mutane ("taɓawa") waɗanda zasu iya yin hulɗa da mutanen da suka kamu.
An yi amfani da aikace-aikacen da yawa ko kuma an gabatar da su, kuma an ba su goyon baya na gwamnati a wasu yankuna da kuma hukumomi.
An gina wasu tsarin da za su iya yin amfani da su wajen bin diddigin lambobin sadarwa.
An yi tambaya game da batun tsare sirri, musamman ma game da tsarin da ke dogara da bin diddigin yanayin masu amfani da aikace-aikacen.
Wani zaɓi da ba ya ɓata sirrin mutum ya ƙunshi yin amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rikodin yadda mai amfani yake kusa da wata wayar hannu.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun sanar da cewa za su haɗa ayyukan don tallafawa waɗannan aikace-aikacen na Bluetooth kai tsaye zuwa tsarin aiki na Android da iOS.
A kasar Sin, gwamnatin kasar Sin, tare da Alipay, ta kaddamar da aikace-aikacen da ke ba 'yan ƙasa damar duba idan sun yi hulɗa da masu cutar COVID-19.
Ana amfani da shi a birane fiye da 200 a kasar Sin. A Singapore, ana amfani da shi da wani app mai suna TraceTogether.
Kungiyar IT ta ci gaba da samar da wannan app, ta saki shi a matsayin tushen budewa kuma za a mika shi ga gwamnatoci. Arewacin Macedonia ta kaddamar da "StopKorona!", wani app na Bluetooth don bin diddigin bayyanar da mutanen da ke da cutar da kuma ba da amsa mai sauri ga hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da kuma Ma'aikatar Kiwon Lafiya ne suka samar da wannan aikace-aikacen.
Har zuwa 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, aikace-aikacen yana jiran amincewar Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta bayyana cewa aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba yana cikin ci gaba da ci gaba kuma zai kasance a cikin 'yan makonni don rarrabawa.
Australia da New Zealand suna la'akari da aikace-aikacen da ke dogara da aikace-aikacen TraceTogether na Singapore da yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha na son gabatar da aikace-aikacen geofencing ga marasa lafiyar da aka gano COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow; an tsara wannan aikace-aikacen don tabbatar da cewa ba sa barin gida.
Ross Anderson, wani farfesa a jami'ar Cambridge, ya ambata wasu matsaloli masu amfani da za su iya faruwa a tsarin da aka yi amfani da shi, wanda ya haɗa da rashin tabbataccen sakamako da kuma yiwuwar rashin tasiri idan an yi amfani da bayanan da aka yi amfani da su a cikin ƙananan ƙananan mutane.
Don magance damuwar game da ɓarna ko ɓarna na aikace-aikacen "coronavirus", Apple ya sanya takunkumi kan nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi waɗanda zasu iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da suka shafi coronavirus zuwa App Store, wato, iyakance kawai ga ƙungiyoyi "masu izini" ko masu suna.
