Ƙungiyar Masu Kare Sirri a MIT Media Lab ta haɓaka SafePaths, dandamali don amfani da fasahar kare sirrin yayin tattarawa da amfani da wurare ko bayanan haɗakarwa don bin diddigin yaduwar COVID-19.
Wannan ya dogara ne akan binciken da aka yi daga takardar farin "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" da aka saki a watan Maris na 2020. Wani irin wannan shiri shi ne dandamali na SafeTrace na Enigma MPC, kamfanin da ke bunkasa fasahar tsare sirri kuma an kafa shi ne a MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace yana amfani da ingantaccen fasahar kayan aiki don bawa masu amfani damar raba wurare da bayanan kiwon lafiya masu mahimmanci tare da sauran masu amfani da jami'an ba tare da yin sadaukar da sirrin bayanan ba.
